title: El Camino Real de los Tejas National Historic Trail: Photos & Multimedia
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia             Photos & Multimedia              Exhibits - View outdoor exhibits at various sites along El Camino Real de los Tejas NHT. Take the virtual journey and then visit the site!             Take A Photographic Journey of the Trail - this incredible journey starts in Mexico, spans Texas, and ends at the trail's eastern terminus in Louisiana.             Photo Gallery - Go here to see and download El Camino de los Tejas images       Mission San Fransisco de la Espada in Texas Christopher Talbot
